  memoryId: guitar
  objectName: Guitar
  objectSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bbb245fb0a2d841df90286b4edb786f8, type: 3}
  glowSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 19ff9d2db23c748f180e5c1ea218991e, type: 3}
  shortDescription: "Robert's acoustic guitar. There's a massive crack down the back
    of the neck. It's broken."
  fullStory: "The 10th anniversary. Martha says he wrote her a beautiful song. The
    guitar neck is cracked. These two facts cannot both be true."
  marthaContext: "The 10th anniversary was the proudest moment \u2014 he stayed up
    all night writing a song, played it at sunrise in his dress shirt, coffee going
    cold. It was beautiful. The most beautiful thing she had ever heard."
  davidContext: "David doesn\u2019t know what happened with the guitar. Robert stopped
    playing one day and never said why. Martha never said why. David learned not
    to push on that door. Whatever happened, it\u2019s between Robert and Martha."
